sentences: Delegates returned from their break on Sunday to find that what little momentum existed at the end of last week had dissipated.

Some observers expressed frustration at the lack of progress in the contact groups on adverse effects and the IPCC TAR, and noted that one exasperated delegate had stormed out of discussions on the SCCF.
They noted that the CDM Executive Board had a productive weekend addressing baseline methodologies and reviewing a series of project proposals.
